			     SEMEVAL-2013
			    -------------

               TASK 12: Multilingual Word Sense Disambiguation

In order to participate in the multilingual WSD task, you need to:

   1. join our Google group
   2. download the trial data from the task webpage
   5. get BabelNet 
   6. download the test data from the task website 
   7. upload the results (up to three different system runs)
   8. write a paper

--------
BabelNet
--------

All resources related to BabelNet -- i.e., dumps, API, etc. can be found
here:

http://babelnet.org/

---------------
Test/trial data
---------------

Trial and test data can be found on the task webpage:

 http://www.cs.york.ac.uk/semeval-2013/task12/index.php?id=data

------------
Google group
------------

Participants MUST join the task Google group:

 http://groups.google.com/group/semeval13-multilingual-wsd

